# 🥁 Kids Drum Game

A fun, interactive drum kit game designed for kids!  
Built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Click or press keys to play different drum sounds
- Colorful and responsive buttons
- Easy to use for children
- Sound effects for each drum pad

---

## 🧩 Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- Web Audio API

---

## 🎮 How to Play

1. Open the website or run `index.html` in your browser.
2. Click on the drum buttons or press the corresponding keys on your keyboard.
3. Enjoy the beats!

